        <abstract> 
<p>Have received <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>. It will interest not only botanists but zoologists and biologists.</p> 
            <p>Ten years ago AD-P encountered great opposition when he started teaching Darwinism at Zurich. Now all except old Oswald Heer call themselves Darwinists.</p>
        </abstract>
